{"tid":2195462,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【新股IPO】樂享互動擬周四招股　集資15.6億元","createTime":"2020-09-09T07:51:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-09T07:51:33.000Z","uid":323911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"436b3765acc8b572897eab7e6cd62bff00030b71","tid":2195462,"uid":323911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T07:51:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://inews.hket.com/article/2746028/%E3%80%90%E6%96%B0%E8%82%A1IPO%E3%80%91%E6%A8%82%E4%BA%AB%E4%BA%92%E5%8B%95%E6%93%AC%E5%91%A8%E5%9B%9B%E6%8B%9B%E8%82%A1%E3%80%80%E9%9B%86%E8%B3%8715.6%E5%84%84%E5%85%83\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finews.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2746028%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2582%25A1IPO%25E3%2580%2591%25E6%25A8%2582%25E4%25BA%25AB%25E4%25BA%2592%25E5%258B%2595%25E6%2593%25AC%25E5%2591%25A8%25E5%259B%259B%25E6%258B%259B%25E8%2582%25A1%25E3%2580%2580%25E9%259B%2586%25E8%25B3%258715.6%25E5%2584%2584%25E5%2585%2583&d=Yvf7L03l0%2FKFASkGPCPwgxSGsERVwMiaoyLN1PNQjS0%3D&h=d3a4c307\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://inews.hket.com/article/2746028/%E3%80%90%E6%96%B0%E8%82%A1IPO%E3%80%91%E6%A8%82%E4%BA%AB%E4%BA%92%E5%8B%95%E6%93%AC%E5%91%A8%E5%9B%9B%E6%8B%9B%E8%82%A1%E3%80%80%E9%9B%86%E8%B3%8715.6%E5%84%84%E5%85%83</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static01-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2745000/2746028/080920_LOK_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic01-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2745000%2F2746028%2F080920_LOK_1024.jpg&h=7ee5eb3f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n樂享互動已通過上市聆訊，消息指，樂享互動已開始投資者路演，將於周四招股，計劃集資2億美元（約15.6億港元）。樂享互動於2008年成立，是中國一間媒體營銷服務商，為行業客戶分析及分銷的產品，並提供效果類營銷服務，幫助行業客戶獲得用戶。樂享互動聯席保薦人為中信建投、招商及交銀。<br />\n<br />\n截至今年3月底， 樂享互動建立的應用組合覆蓋超過十個種類（如遊戲、視頻及工具應用）；集團的網絡文學產品包括覆蓋69個文學類別的681多冊網絡書籍；而集團的Html 5遊戲產品包括超過 157個覆蓋RPG、戰略、動作及冒險種類的Html 5遊戲。<br />\n<br />\n截至今年3月底，集團溢利按年增91.9%至2051萬元（人民幣，下同）；收入按年增71.5%至1.67億元。"}]}